data.description: Waterfront on the Middle Saluda River. Approx. 267 ft of river frontage. Excellent fishing river. This nearly 3 acres includes a 1600 sq ft house in need of repair or build your own. The old railroad bed from the famed Swamp Rabbit is part of this property. 9 miles to Downtown Travelers Rest. 30 minutes to Hendersonville, NC , 45 minutes to Brevard, NC and 30 minutes to Downtown Greenville
